<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sidhi Bharti portal 2025</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="desain-logo-vector-product-google-600nw-2511045883-removebg-preview.png"
        type="image/x-icon">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">
    <script src="/javascript/script.js"></script>
    <!-- <script src="hide/express.js"></script> -->
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="box1">
            <form action="/create" method="post">
                <div class="p">
                    <div class="p_1">
                        <label for="A_name">Name:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="A_name" placeholder="Enter your hero name" name="name" required>
                        <br><br>
                        <label for="Email">Email:</label>
                        <input type="email" id="Email" placeholder="Enter your Email" name="gmail" required>
                        <br><br>
                        <label for="gen">Gender:</label>
                        <input type="radio" name="gender" value="male" id="gen">Male
                        <input type="radio" name="gender" value="female" id="gen">Female
                        <input type="radio" name="gender" value="other" id="gen">Other
                    </div>
                    <div class="p_2">
                        <input type="text" name="image" id="p_image">

                        <label for="p_image">Hero's_Image</label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="q">
                    <h2 title=""Go ahead and share your info — your privacy is safe with us!"">Note:</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Hero should be in costume in the Hero's image.</li>
                        <li>Hero's name starting or ending with symbols (@, #, !, _) or numbers will not be considered.
                        </li>
                        <li>Hero's image should be in .png format.</li>
                        <li>No sidekicks allowed in the image. This is solo glory only.</li>
                        <li>No sunglasses indoors. You're a hero, not a DJ.</li>
                        <li>If your hero glows, reduce brightness. We're still recovering from last year’s Ultraviolet
                            Incident.</li>
                        <li>If your hero is invisible, please do not upload a blank .png (nice try though).</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="submit">
                    <input type="submit" value="submit">

                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>

</html>